    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Not a Smart Hero archetype, Intelligence 13+, Level 2+</p><p>You have sharpened your wits to a razor's edge and turned your mind into the greatest weapon of all.</p><ul><li><p>You gain 2 Genius points. You can enact any plan you know by spending 1 Genius point. Genius points recharge when you finish a long rest. Your Plan DC formula is 8 + your Intelligence modifier + your proficiency bonus.</p></li><li><p>You learn two plans from the Shared Plans list for Smart Heroes.</p></li><li><p>You can only use shared plan enhancements up to Level 1.</p></li></ul>",
